{
  "npc": {
    "id": "npc.aldo",
    "name": "Aldo",
    "role": "mentor",
    "shortDescription": "守灯人。脸上有大片伤疤，左手少了两根手指。再不下水。",
    "dialogRoot": {
      "id": "aldo.root",
      "text": "黎明前的鸢尾湾。雾还没散。Aldo 坐在长椅上，看着海。他没回头。\n\n「准备好了？」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "ready",
          "label": "准备好了。",
          "next": "aldo.briefing",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "not_yet",
          "label": "还差一点。",
          "next": "aldo.look_around",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "morning",
          "label": "（坐下，跟他看一会儿海）",
          "next": "aldo.harbor_morning",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "dialogs": {
    "aldo.briefing": {
      "id": "aldo.briefing",
      "text": "「让我看看你的装备。」\n\nAldo 接过去，挨个检查。\n\n「你导师的装备，我帮你保养了这么多年。今天你去东礁那个老沉船把这个浮标取回来。算是你在这片海的初次潜水，简单。」\n\n他停顿了一下。\n\n「记住：氧气是时间，氮气是债。慢慢上来，别贪。」\n\n「四样东西你要盯紧——体力，氧气，理智，氮气。前两样你能直接看到。第三样你自己感觉。第四样会找你算账。」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "depart_east",
          "label": "出海到东礁（初次潜水）。",
          "next": "end",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" },
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "setFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_briefed" },
            { "kind": "startDive", "zoneId": "zone.east_reef" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "open_chart",
          "label": "（摊开海图，挑一个潜点）",
          "next": "end",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" },
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "openChart" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_mentor",
          "label": "你认识我导师？",
          "next": "aldo.about_mentor"
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.harbor_morning": {
      "id": "aldo.harbor_morning",
      "text": "你在长椅另一头坐下。海面有风，雾往外退。\n\n「潮位正好。」Aldo 朝海图桌那边抬了抬下巴，「今天去哪，你自己挑——那些坐标，你现在比我熟。」\n\n他顿了顿。\n\n「带够气。回来吃饭。」",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "open_chart",
          "label": "（摊开海图，挑一个潜点）",
          "next": "end",
          "effects": [
            { "kind": "openChart" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "ask_mentor",
          "label": "你认识我导师？",
          "next": "aldo.about_mentor"
        },
        {
          "id": "leave",
          "label": "（再坐一会儿，然后起身）",
          "next": "end"
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.about_mentor": {
      "id": "aldo.about_mentor",
      "text": "Aldo 沉默了很久。\n\n「他是上一代最后一个还敢去深处的人。」\n\n他没说更多。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "back",
          "label": "（沉默地点头）",
          "next": "aldo.briefing",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "notHasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        },
        {
          "id": "back_morning",
          "label": "（沉默地点头）",
          "next": "aldo.harbor_morning",
          "visibleIf": { "kind": "hasFlag", "flag": "flag.tutorial_complete" }
        }
      ]
    },
    "aldo.look_around": {
      "id": "aldo.look_around",
      "text": "「随你。但太阳一出，潮位就涨。」\n\n你在港口走了一圈。气瓶师 Otto 在仓库门口给一只气瓶上压力，没抬头。打捞商 Mira 的柜台已经开了——可以去找她出手东西。海鸥在桅杆上叫。\n\n回到长椅时，Aldo 还在那个位置。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "now_ready",
          "label": "现在准备好了。",
          "next": "aldo.briefing"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
